.TH BWFALL 1 "2026-03-01" "bwfall 1.0.0" "User Commands"
.SH NAME
bwfall \- Binary Waterfall CLI - Raw Data Media Player
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B bwfall
[\fIOPTIONS\fR] [\fIFILE\fR]
.SH DESCRIPTION
.B bwfall
reads any binary file byte-by-byte and interprets the raw data as audio (PCM samples) and/or visual output (scrolling colored terminal display). No format parsing, no headers — just pure binary data transformed into an audio-visual experience.
.SH OPTIONS
.TP
.BR \-i ", " \-\-input " " \fIFILE\fR
Input file (or use stdin)
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-audio
Disable audio output
.TP
.BR \-\-no\-visual
Disable visual output
.TP
.BR \-s ", " \-\-speed " " \fIFLOAT\fR
Playback speed multiplier (default: 1.0)
.TP
.BR \-l ", " \-\-loop
Loop playback indefinitely
.TP
.BR \-p ", " \-\-pause
Start in paused state
.TP
.BR \-\-start " " \fIBYTES\fR
Start offset in bytes
.TP
.BR \-\-length " " \fIBYTES\fR
Number of bytes to play
.TP
.BR \-\-audio\-mode " " \fIMODE\fR
Audio mode: pcm|freq|fm|noise (default: pcm)
.TP
.BR \-\-sample\-rate " " \fIHZ\fR
Sample rate in Hz (default: 44100)
.TP
.BR \-\-channels " " \fIN\fR
Number of channels 1-2 (default: 1)
.TP
.BR \-\-volume " " \fI0-100\fR
Output volume (default: 80)
.TP
.BR \-\-visual\-mode " " \fIMODE\fR
Visual mode: waterfall|hex|binary|matrix|spectrum|waveform
.TP
.BR \-\-colormap " " \fIMAP\fR
Color map: rainbow|heat|grayscale|binary
.TP
.BR \-\-fps " " \fIN\fR
Target frames per second (default: 30)
.TP
.BR \-v ", " \-\-verbose
Show verbose output
.TP
.BR \-\-stats
Show live statistics overlay
.TP
.BR \-h ", " \-\-help
Show help message
.TP
.BR \-\-version
Show version information
.SH EXAMPLES
.TP
Play a binary file:
.B bwfall /bin/ls
.TP
Pipe random data:
.B cat /dev/urandom | bwfall \-\-speed 0.5
.TP
Visual only (no audio):
.B bwfall \-\-no\-audio \-\-visual\-mode matrix /usr/bin/python3
.TP
Audio only (no visual):
.B bwfall \-\-no\-visual /boot/vmlinuz
.SH INTERACTIVE CONTROLS
.TP
.B SPACE
Pause/Resume
.TP
.BR q ", " ESC
Quit
.TP
.BR → ", " l
Seek forward
.TP
.BR ← ", " h
Seek backward
.TP
.BR ↑ ", " k
Increase speed
.TP
.BR ↓ ", " j
Decrease speed
.TP
.B +
Increase volume
.TP
.B \-
Decrease volume
.TP
.B r
Restart from beginning
.TP
.B m
Toggle mute
.TP
.B v
Cycle visual mode
.TP
.B c
Cycle colormap
